Package: PeakGeneNet
Type: Package
Title: Integration of Epigenomic Peaks to Genes through Correlation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Anne", "Weitzel",
      email = "weitzela@umich.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7615-6357")
    )
  )
Description: This package identifies distal regulatory links to gene expression through correlation of all possible peak connections within 1Mb of the genes TSS.
    Four link types are considered: distal peaks to promomoter peaks, distal peaks to genes, promoter peaks to promoter peaks, and promoter peaks to genes.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
